•Tonto Dikeh Popular Nigerian actress, Tonto Dikeh has taken to social media to talk about her desire to have a child again. The actress shared this desire on a post on her instagram page. The actress shared a no-makeup photo of herself showing a pimple on her face. In her caption, she noted that her first pregnancy took away all her impurities. According to her, she was super excited and grateful for the impurities her first pregnancy took away. She said that now that she is without a child she is back to fighting a very stubborn pimple. On the post, Dikeh added that she thinks it is time to get pregnant again. She then teased, asking her baby if he is ready. The actress shared other no-makeup photos of herself on her Instagram page. (Tori) 